d in a Mass Embrace, suddenly thrown into the dangerous and ruthless vampire politics of Seattle. Tensions between the factions in Seattle are at an all-time high, and this unsanctioned attack throws the status quo into chaos. An inquest is called in order to get to the bottom of the mystery, and you\u2019re the star witness\u2026 whether you like it or not..", "summary": "Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 is the successor to the iconic RPG Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines. Set in a Seattle faithfully reimagined in the World of Darkness, Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 features reactive storytelling, fast-paced melee combat, and intriguing characters with their own hidden motives.\n\nCreated in an act of vampire insurrection, your existence ignites a blood war among the vampire factions who run Seattle. To survive, you\u2019ll choose a clan and enter into uneasy alliances with competing factions in a world which will react to every choice you make. Unleash your supernatural powers against your prey, but be mindful of your surroundings at all times or run the risk of breaking the Masquerade (the absolute law of secrecy that keeps Vampire society hidden from humanity).", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 19, "name": "Horror"}, {"id": 43, "name": "Mystery"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2", "videos": [{"id": 35776, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "5MzIbWbMFi0", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5MzIbWbMFi0", "title": "Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 'Come Dance' Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5MzIbWbMFi0/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 27927, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "cFLXoGzXxJc", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cFLXoGzXxJc", "title": "Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cFLXoGzXxJc/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 37345, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "95H0zhZOv4w", "url":